OL,3,CMurder charge after man found dead on
OL,4,Crooftop garden
OL,6,FA 50-year-old has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder following the death of a man
OL,8,Fwho was found on a rooftop garden in
OL,9,FBristol.
OL,11,FAnthony Clemmings, 54, was discovered
OL,12,Fby a member of the public on Redcliff
OL,13,FStreet on the morning on Tuesday 5
OL,14,FMay. His family are being supported by
OL,15,Fspecially trained officers, Avon and
OL,16,FSomerset Police have said.
OL,18,FMr Clemmings, known as Tony, was
OL,19,Fdescribed as a 'much-loved son,
OL,20,Fbrother and uncle', by his family.
