OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1778602268
OL,3,CMurder charge after man found dead on
OL,4,Crooftop garden
OL,6,FNigel Lubban, of no fixed abode, was
OL,7,Farrested in the West Midlands on
OL,8,FFriday 8 May and has since been
OL,9,Fcharged with murder.
OL,11,FHe has been remanded in custody ahead
OL,12,Fof an appearance at Bristol
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court tomorrow, 11 May.
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Laura
OL,16,FMiller, of the Major Crime
OL,17,FInvestigation Team, said: "The Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service has authorised a
OL,19,Fmurder charge against Nigel Lubban.
OL,26,@yD@[OU
